[SN]TITLE[SN]
Alex Sandro: Brazilian joins Juventus from Porto in £18m deal

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Brazil left-back Alex Sandro has signed for Italian champions Juventus from Porto for £18.6m (26m euros) on a five-year deal.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 24-year-old, with six caps for his country, has been linked with Manchester United and Real Madrid in the past.
Juventus begin their Serie A campaign at home against Udinese on Sunday.
They won the league and cup double last season but lost the Champions League final to Barcelona.
